Lvl 6 -> 7

Goal: The password for the next level is stored somewhere on the server and has all of the following properties:

owned by user bandit7
owned by group bandit6
33 bytes in size

Command used:

find / -type f -user bandit7 -group bandit6 -size 33c 2>/dev/null
cat /var/lib/dpkg/info/bandit7.password

//
'find /' -> Search the entire system
-type f -> Human-Readable
-user bandit7 -> Owned by bandit7
-group bandit6 -> Owned by group bandit6
-size 33c -> 33 bytes
2>/dev/null -> removes(transfers) permission denied errors (into another)

